The paper is primarily focused on face parsing, which is a computer vision task, and hence, it is most likely to belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new dataset and a new network architecture, which involves machine learning techniques, making it likely to belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-categories. The paper also deals with image processing and analysis, which falls under the cs.MM (Multimedia) sub-category. Finally, the paper involves natural language processing techniques for describing the proposed framework and dataset, which falls under the cs.CL (Computation and Language) sub-category.
